    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1094480,
    "dDurationMs": 6720,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "community as well as like key partners. \nAnd we work closely for example with like  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1101200,
    "dDurationMs": 8800,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "people in the industry that worked on \nand other aspects to get this right."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1110000,
    "dDurationMs": 6960,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And so with authorization in MCP, what you can do \nis you can basically provide the private context  "
    } ]
